name: Manulife Smart International Dividend ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide a steady flow of income and long-term capital appreciation. Fund investing primarily in a diversified portfolio of international dividend paying securities. Any exposure that the portion of the portfolio of the ETF attributable to the Unhedged Units may have to foreign currencies will not be hedged back to the Canadian dollar.
